code: A watercolor of a resplendent golden phoenix with magnificent radiant feathers in the style of vibrant abstract expressionism. It elegantly perches on the rugged edge of a craggy cliff overlooking a vast, serene desert under a stunning twilight sky, casting an enchanting warm glow from its wings, amidst a surreal landscape of towering wind-carved rock formations and mesmerizing floating glass orbs.

A detailed watercolor of a radiant golden phoenix with fiery flaming feathers in the style of surrealism. It is majestically soaring above the crumbling rooftops in an ancient, mystical city on a stormy, overcast day, gracefully scattering glowing embers from its ethereal wings, amidst an environment of twisting, towering spires and shimmering, floating lanterns.
